» World’s Biggest Beef Buffet!! Heart Attack Challenge in Argentina!

🧀 *CHARCUTERIE BOARD*
🥩 *RIBEYE STEAK*

🍖 *SMOKED BEEF RIBS* (+ 2 Side Dishes)
